# Privacy Policy

**SayDay App** respects your privacy.

## Data Collection
- The app requires access to your microphone to record audio as part of its core functionality.
- Audio recordings are stored locally on your device and are not transmitted to our servers or any third party.

## Data Usage
- Audio data is used only for the features provided by the app (e.g., playback, saving recordings).
- We do not use your audio data for advertising or analytics.

## Permissions
- The app requests the RECORD_AUDIO permission to enable audio recording features.

## Contact
If you have any questions about your privacy, please contact us at: [kgbonlain@gmail.com]

